subject: Basketball
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: Samardo Samuels scored all 14 of his points in the final 16 minutes, leading St. Benedict’s (14-1) to a 55-52 victory against Rice (10-2), which is ranked No. 12 in the USA Today poll.
